\frametitle{Don't use tables for layout} 
\bi
\li Old HTML didn't have layout facilities, so tables were used.
\li Tables aren't meant for layout.
\li The table code becomes complicated fast.
\li Formatting is done cell by cell.
\li Presentation is tied to data.
\li Table-based layouts are hard to change.
\li Table-based layouts cause problems for screen readers.
\li Table-based layouts do not adapt well to phones and tablets.
\ei
